I believe these changes will positively influence both 6879's mental and physical health. This will shift 6879's focus as a result, motivating them and will influence them to subconsciously break the cycle of 6879-A production.

Please reply with your thoughts,

Zac

P.S. I shall make enquiries regarding GoI-101 and GoI-386[[footnote]]"Dr. Wondertainment"[[/footnote]] if 6879's mental health improves.
